      <title>策略师削减了S＆amp; P 500预测，但仍期待集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/strategists-cut-s-p-500-forecasts-but-still-expect-a-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街最可靠的公牛中有三只承认，他们对今年的S＆amp; P 500指数的估计过于乐观。但是他们仍然认为，股票将在2025年剩余的四分之三中集会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/strategists-cut-s-p-500-forecasts-but-still-expect-a-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 16:07:26 GMT</pubDate>
